    "syllabus": {
        "zh": "1.了解有關社區工作的基本概念及發展（知識）<br>2.了解社區工作的實務與工作技巧（技能）<br>3.了解社區工作的價值與原則（態度）<br>4.了解社區工作的理論與模型（其他）<br>5.了解專業社區工作的未來發展（其他）",
        "en": "1. Understand the basic concepts and developments of community<br>Work<br>2. Understand the practical and work skills of community work<br>3. Understand the values and principles of community work<br>4. Understand the theory and model of community work<br>5. Future development of professional community work"
